content.description: This job reads data from ACX Guidewire DB and loads it into the Metal staging tables. It follows a one-to-one mapping with no transformations.
content.name: cdi_map_acx_coverage_item_metal_load

select
	a.SystemId,
	ParentId,
	a.CMMContainer,
	Id,
	Status,
	CoverageItemCd,
	FullTermAmt,
	FullTermManualAmt,
	FinalPremiumAmt,
	WrittenPremiumAmt,
	EarnedAmt,
	SequenceNumber,
	ItemDesc,
	PrevFinalAmt,
	PrevWrittenAmt,
	TransactionCommissionAmt,
	ShortRateAmt,
	FutureStatusCd,
	DriverIdRef,
	NumFamilies,
	AdditionalPlanChargePct,
	NumOfUnits,
	Manufacturer,
	Model,
	ModelYr,
	VehBodyTypeCd,
	EngineType,
	EngineDesc,
	StatedAmt,
	BreakageCovInd,
	OutboardMotorVal,
	TrailerType,
	TrailerValue,
	UnattachedEquipType,
	UnattachedEquipValue,
	EngineCC,
	InExpOper,
	VehicleVIN,
	ResidencyDet,
	SchoolName,
	ItemType,
	Horsepower,
	Length,
	OperatingArea,
	PBHullDed,
	PBHullValue,
	PBMotorValue,
	PBPersonalEffectValue,
	MoreThan1Eng,
	Identical2ndEng,
	PBLiability,
	PBMedPayment,
	PBAgreedAmount,
	PBDtLastSurvey,
	PBHullMaterial,
	PBMaxSpeed,
	PBWaterNav,
	PBAICount,
	PBEngineYear1,
	PBEngineModel1,
	PBEngineHP1,
	PBEngineFuel1,
	PBEngineYear2,
	PBEngineModel2,
	PBEngineHP2,
	PBEngineFuel2,
	PBAI1,
	PBAIName1,
	PBAIStreet1,
	PBAICity1,
	PBAIState1,
	PBAIZip1,
	PBAILoanNum1,
	PBAI2,
	PBAIName2,
	PBAIStreet2,
	PBAICity2,
	PBAIState2,
	PBAIZip2,
	PBAILoanNum2,
	CommercialTowingInd,
	AgreedAmountOutInd,
	CoastGuardCertInd,
	EducationalExpInd,
	ShipToShoreInd,
	MarineCompassInd,
	DepthFinderInd,
	VaporDetectInd,
	CO2HalonFireInd,
	RadarSystemInd,
	LoranGPSInd,
	HullDed,
	Diesel,
	HullValue,
	OutBoardMotVal,
	TrailerDesc,
	TrailerVal,
	UnattachEquipDesc,
	UnattachEquipValue,
	ParentItemNumber,
	RatingInd,
	RowId,
	ClassCd
FROM coverageitem a
inner join advrxxchangedbeans b
on a.Systemid = b.Systemid
and a.CmmContainer = b.CmmContainer
and b.CmmContainer in ('Policy','Application')
where CONCAT(b.adddt, ' ', substr(b.addtm, 1, 8))>= $LASTRUNTIME
